An aborigen chifetain says to his tribe:<br>- We must make an atomic bomb!<br>All aborigens supports him. Some men chopped the biggest baobab, filled it with powder, made a cap and a wick.<br>- Let's nuke Monte-Carlo!<br>- Why Monte-Carlo?<br>- We dont know any other cities!<br>Marked "To Monte-Carlo" on the bomb. All aborigens standing near the bomb, chifetain is firing the wick, the whole tribe is counting: 3, 2, 1...<br>Bomb has exploded. Blood, fire and corpses are everywhere. Chifetain, lost his legs, crawling and saying:<br>- Holy fuck, if we've got THIS in our island, what kind of mess they got in Monte-Carlo...